results.name: Rod Laver 'White Team College Gold'
results.story: The adidas Rod Laver ‘White Team College Gold’ showcases OG-inspired color blocking on the retro silhouette named after the Australian tennis great. The white textile upper is fortified with a tonal leather eyestay, light grey suede toe guard and an orange leather heel tab. The latter features an embossed adidas Trefoil with Rod Laver branding. A vintage off-white finish is applied to the midsole, supported underfoot by a pivot-point rubber outsole

results.name: Terrex Two Ultra Primeblue 'Scarlet Hazy Sky'
Wmns Sleek Super 'Leopard'
results.story: The adidas women’s Sleek Super ‘Leopard’ outfits the lifestyle silhouette with audacious details intended to make a statement. An oversized Trefoil lace jewel shines in metallic gold, nearly stealing the spotlight from the leopard print that covers virtually every inch of the leather upper. The all-over design is interrupted by a tan suede heel tab and an adidas logo window on the lateral eyestay. An exaggerated platform midsole anchors the streamlined upper.

results.name: Wmns Terrex Two Ultra Primeblue 'Black Solar Yellow'
Superstar 'Off White Collegiate Gold'
results.story: The adidas Superstar ‘Off White Collegiate Gold’ treats the classic silhouette to an elevated makeover, highlighted by a genuine leather lining and cork insole. Off-white leather is utilized on the upper, accented with a heel tab and signature three-stripes in Collegiate Gold. The sneaker’s iconic rubber shell toe is joined by additional heritage details, including midfoot perforations, tonal stitching and a Superstar wordmark stamped in gold on the lateral side. Underfoot, a herringbone traction outsole delivers reliable grip.

results.name: Wmns QT Racer Sport 'White Semi Night Flash'
Superstar 'Off White Maroon'
results.story: The adidas Superstar ‘Off White Maroon’ dresses the iconic shell-toed sneaker in a simple two-tone color scheme that speaks to the shoe’s basketball roots. A subtle ivory tone distinguishes the leather upper, contrasted by burgundy accents on the heel tab and serrated three-stripes. The latter is flanked by a Superstar wordmark stamped in metallic gold lettering on the lateral side panel. The low-top sits on a vintage off-white rubber cupsole, featuring a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Terrex Two Ultra Primeblue 'Black Solar Yellow'
Superstar 'Off White Collegiate Green'
results.story: The adidas Superstar ‘Off White Collegiate Green’ updates the sneaker icon in a traditional two-tone palette seemingly lifted from the brand’s early ‘70s archive. The heel tab and signature three-stripes are rendered in a forest green hue, allowing the details to stand out against an off-white leather backdrop. Elevated details include a leather-lined interior and a shock-absorbing cork insole. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a herringbone tread originally designed for the hardwood.

results.name: Stella McCartney x Wmns Barricade Boost 'Acid Orange'
adidas Harden Vol. 5 Nets
results.story: The adidas Harden Vol. 5 Futurenatural ‘Welcome to BKLYN’ showcase a neutral white and black palette that syncs up with the signature colors of the Brooklyn Nets. Breathable white textile is utilized on the upper, accented with contrasting black synthetic overlays and seamlessly fused to the data-informed rubber outsole. In lieu of a traditional foam midsole, the sneaker makes use of drop-in midsole that combines adidas Boost with a Lightstrike carrier for added stability and torsional support.
